step 1:

get your database name , get your password 

you can reset the password inside 

ALTER USER postgres WITH PASSWORD "postgres123";



step 2:

create your .env file 

inside !



DATABASE_URL=postgresql+psycopg://postgres:postgres123@localhost:5432/YOUR_DATABASE_NAME




step 3 
(assuming .venv was created already!)

activate your environment!

source .venv/bin/activate 




step 4

Install packages 

pip install fastapi uvicorn sqlalchemy "psycopg[binary]" python-dotenv

